data.description: This immaculate home boasts 4 bedrooms and 2.5 bathrooms sitting on just shy of a half acre lot.This 3,145 Sq ft house will amaze you with its high ceilings, beautiful kitchen, large master suite with double vanities, and huge walk in shower. Spacious rooms throughout the home, as well as a sunroom.Outside you'll be amazed by the new large above groundpool that was built in July 2023 and is surrounded by a new deck.Two 12x24 foot workshops wired with electricity are also in the backyard.The green unit has a window unit and is currently used as a office. The covered patio with a built in BBQ grill, along with the pool makes this home perfect for entertaining family and friends. Don't miss out on this amazing home, and schedule a tour today! Home has been appraised  by Hub City Appraisals.The opinion of value was 335k.
